content.p: This page sets out the University's right to withdraw an offer of admission to one of its programmes if certain conditions are met. Its content is primarily aimed at prospective students to all of the UK, China and Malaysia campuses. Includes: conditions of admission; the University's right to withdraw an offer Admission queries UNUK Admission queries UNNC Admissions queries UNM Quality-Manual-Enquiries@nottingham.ac.uk Portland Building, University of Nottingham University Park Nottingham, NG7 2RD
